data.description: AMAZING VIEWS FROM EACH AND EVERY WINDOW of this quality custom built home. Overlooking Netarts Bay and featuring ocean views including Three Arch Rocks makes this a must see.  Stunning 2.14 acre lot with generous 3,362 SqFt home and huge 1,800 sq foot detached shop that will accommodate your boats, cars, and toys.  Entertainer's kitchen with 3 pantries and plenty of storage. Cozy wood burning stove in living room and a dining nook all overlooking the surrounding panorama view. Seller will consider a flooring allowance credit at closing. First time on the market (one owner) in a great neighborhood.  Guaranteed visits from wildlife from the surrounding nature which frames the property.
